subject: Tour de France (Bicycle Race)
World Cup 2010 (Soccer)
Bicycles and Bicycling
lead_paragraph: With Cadel Evans, Andy Schleck and Alberto Contador in the top spots after a shakeout at the Tour de France, the psychological jockeying has begun.
